high_descs: Move to the toilet to the left of the shower

Move to the counter in between the two sinks
Put the roll onto the counter

Move to the counter in between the two sinks again
Put the full roll behind the empty one on the counter

put the toilet roll on to the counter between the two sinks
turn left and go to the toilet
pick up the toilet roll that is on the water tank of the toilet
